- Deferred deduplicating the controls StatementByComponent.vue with the SSP-side duplicate because the SSP-area refactor is not present in this worktree; only the controls copy was aligned to volt components.
- Preserved the existing system-security-plan shared create/edit forms and SystemImplementationComponentCreateForm call sites; this task only updates how the controls drawer invokes and surrounds them.
- Left evidence dashboard filter construction in the parent drawer because the computed filter, label-condition derivation, and dashboard create payload are existing contracts shared by the linking flow.
